# 🎞️ CSS Animations – Millisoft Project Folder

This folder contains a collection of **CSS animation exercises** created to demonstrate different types of visual effects using only HTML and CSS. These are part of the broader Millisoft front-end learning and practice repository.

---

## 📌 What's Included

Inside this folder, you'll find mini-projects and components that showcase:

- 🔁 Smooth transitions
- ✨ Hover effects (zoom, rotate, scale)
- 🔄 Keyframe animations (slide, bounce, fade-in/out)
- 💡 Button and card animations
- 📱 Responsive interactive UI elements

Each file is standalone and intended for learning, experimentation, or showcasing animation techniques without using JavaScript or external libraries.

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose                        |
|------------|--------------------------------|
| HTML5      | Structure                      |
| CSS3       | Styling and animations         |
| Flexbox    | Layout and positioning         |
| Keyframes  | Custom animations              |
| Transitions & Transforms | Smooth visual effects |
